Value PROTOCOL_VERSION (\d)
Value TIMEOUT (\d+)
Value AUTHENTICATION_RETRIES (\d)
Value SOURCE_INTERFACE (.+)

Start
  ^ip\s+ssh\s+(?:version\s${PROTOCOL_VERSION})?(?:time-out\s+${TIMEOUT}\d)?(?:authentication-retries\s+${AUTHENTICATION_RETRIES}\d)?(?:source-interface\s+${SOURCE_INTERFACE})?\s*$$ -> Record